name: Pokédex - GO
body:
### Welcome to Pokédex - Go
Pokédex - GO is a modern and up-to-date pokédex filled with information and statistics of over 700 pokémon. 

### Credit
I would like to give credit to the following for providing great content, including icons and images.
* [icons8](https://icons8.com/free-ios-7-icons-in-vector/)
* [thenounproject](https://thenounproject.com/)
* [makeappicon](https://makeappicon.com/)
